{"tid":1470583,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"818 紗布遮眼大遊行","createTime":"2019-08-14T05:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T03:32:52.000Z","uid":189799,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"24750b738566a7be2e5bf9f1b7f31b70eac31d80","tid":1470583,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4NvYaTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4NvYaTs.jpg&h=5b6fcc9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4sQpQTa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4sQpQTa.jpg&h=dc2f7684&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵過最平7蚊3個（有更平嘅希望提供地址）<br />\n預計818當日喺地鐵站派發，資金及資源問題，預計買600個度。<br />\n各位都可以自發買黎派，希望到時大約一半人係遮眼遊行。<br />\n聲援被射眼女仔，讓每個人知道黑警射盲左一個女仔。"},{"pid":"03bdc991c09f9a44edf209acc8422bb49138c9a5","tid":1470583,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:56:50.000Z","msg":"Support"},{"pid":"dafd6d69d92ddc3a11a4779bf0e32ba03a22ddee","tid":1470583,"uid":270824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e74dc2e6b671c7bfe104bd14b5e9ed47e982daf","tid":1470583,"uid":303451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"80a6c1ae99d053abc9b639b6a01a17d8b69e4efb","tid":1470583,"uid":218742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:57:41.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"dd6b4e96a924a0f9d55e416a5039d833368629f0","tid":1470583,"uid":189799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:57:48.000Z","msg":"發夢食過幾次催淚彈。<br />\n其實次次都傷唔到黑警，前期一放催淚彈就散。到宜家有滅火隊，黑警一衝，我地都係散。<br />\n<br />\n唔係話勇武派無用，勇武派嘅作用唔係要傷到黑警，而係令黑警做不合理嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n612嘅過份武力，令政府停止修例<br />\n各區放催淚彈，亂拉街坊，打頭<br />\n811 射眼<br />\n<br />\n每件事都係用前線嘅血換番黎。落力宣傳先對得住受傷嘅前線。所以不如咁玩<br />\n<br />\n勇武＞黑警射眼＞宣傳黑警射眼＞勇武<br />\n<br />\n818全民紗布遮眼遊行，之後散水瞓教。少1日勇武，換黎嘅係819各傳媒集中報道遮眼遊行，個個人都知黑警射盲左一個女仔集眼。"},{"pid":"37ffd372bcf6588c37d35ffea4c65b811d67d3fd","tid":1470583,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"或者紙巾都得啦 唔駛特登買<br />\n各適其適 發揮創意"},{"pid":"6b7827f6228bd8fa59ef2eaf145c5d6da3f912f2","tid":1470583,"uid":218742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:58:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cb460c311dfc98238d26ce77c4a0c3edb230eaa","tid":1470583,"uid":238275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:58:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>最緊要 唔好又 益7-11 屈人錢 呢D大財團啊</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8604d011390e8b6c1fcd4d805466aeab99c613","tid":1470583,"uid":279610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:59:27.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"4bbc1515e7e38edf70cdc6cd743abbde3c10fb77","tid":1470583,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:01:49.000Z","msg":"推咗今晚深水埗先啦<br />\n我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"575dcacf2dc54a39bfb450e986e8b0b5a1d53294","tid":1470583,"uid":189799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37ffd372bcf6588c37d35ffea4c65b811d67d3fd","tid":1470583,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"或者紙巾都得啦 唔駛特登買<br />\n各適其適 發揮創意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:02:46.000Z","msg":"同意，各適其適，用喱種嘅目的主要係方便派啫。<br />\n最緊要多人參與。"},{"pid":"5a5b535139aac40c4b9b60503e01d47e27911561","tid":1470583,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit